    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect dependable ride that still looks great on the road and is ready for its next big adventure with a new owner! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it's all set for you to hop in and go. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
