      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, runs like a dream, and the interior is nice and clean. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of love from the road, but overall it's a solid, comfy vehicle that won't let you down. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 32500.0,
