    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously maintained E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the sought-after 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. The chassis remains taut with a reinforced rear subframe and updated bushings, ensuring the iconic MacPherson/multi-link suspension geometry performs as intended. Recently serviced with a focus on mechanical longevity, this driver-focused machine delivers linear power and exceptional tactile feedback. A superb balance of analog engagement and track-bred engineering.",
